      <div type="edition" n="urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.test-eng2" xml:lang="eng">
        <div type="textpart" subtype="book" n="1">
          <div type="textpart" subtype="card" n="1">
            <p>
              <milestone unit="line" n="1"/>
              Sing, O goddess, the anger <note>Greek: <foreign xml:lang="grc">μῆνιν</foreign></note> of Achilles son of Peleus, that brought countless ills upon the Achaeans.
            </p>
            <p>
              <milestone unit="line" n="5"/>
              Many a brave soul <note>The word "soul" here translates <foreign xml:lang="grc">ψυχή</foreign>.</note> did it send hurrying down to Hades, and many a hero did it yield a prey to dogs and vultures.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
